				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Everything to do with actually changing the display has to be done during vblank (unless you turn off rendering) , sprites too, though you can update the shadow OAM ( usually at $0200 in RAM ) at anytime. You can't make a vblank happen: you have to wait for it by polling $2002 ( PPU_STATUS)  for bit7 set, or enable the PPU to activate NMIs on vblank and appropriately act when NMI is triggered.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

						<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
						<tr valign="middle">
