				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">To add to that. What people mean by &quot;forcing vblank&quot; is to turn off all rendering (turn off both sprite and backround rendering, if either is on you cant write to vram at all times). <br /><br />Just make sure you turn it back on during nmi, or your screen will jump for one frame.<br /><br />edit: Also dont poll $2002 for your game logic, it will ocasionally miss frames, causing your game to run irregular.</div>

